    Fascimile </font><font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="3"> of &quot;</font><em><font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="4" color="#0000FF">Mendel's Principles of Heredity. A Defence</font></em><font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="3">&quot;. By W.
    Bateson
    </font>
  </a></p>
    
    <p><a href="http://www.library.adelaide.edu.au/ual/special/fisher.html"><font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="4" color="#0000FF">Fisher,
    Ronald A, - Papers:
    </font><font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="3">University of Adelaide
        </font></a></p>
    
    <p><a href="http://www.mugu.com/galton/index.html"><font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="4" color="#0000FF">Galton, Francis</font></a><font color="#804040" face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="3"> ["Biometrician"]</font></p>
      <p><a href="http://www.stephenjaygould.org/"><font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="4" color="#0000FF">Gould, Stephen Jay</font></a><font color="#804040" face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="3"> [Advocate of hierarchical levels]</font></p>
     
      <p><a href="http://ehlt.flinders.edu.au/english/GA/GAHome.htm">
      <font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="4" color="#0000FF">Grant Allen </font></a> 
      <font color="#804040"><font face="Dutch 801 Roman" size="3">[born Kingston
      1848]</font></font></p>

    
