<h2 class='date-header'><span>Saturday, June 04, 2005</span></h2>

          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='7289728' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='111789943132726848' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='111789943132726848'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://historicabotanica.blogspot.in/2005/06/link-to-brief-biographies-of-botanists.html'>Link to Brief Biographies of Botanists</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-111789943132726848' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<span style="color:#3333ff;">Click </span><a href="http://www.swcoloradowildflowers.com/biographies%20of%20naturalists.htm"><strong><span style="color:#3333ff;">HERE</span></strong></a><span style="color:#3333ff;"> for a link to some botanical biographical notes.</span>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
